casebody.data:
Whitlock et al., Respondents, v. Manhattan Ry. Co., et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 14, 1890.) Appeal from judgment on report of referee.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Davies & Rapallo, for appellants. J. A. Weeks, Jr., for respondents.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs, on opinion in the Werfelman Case, ante, 66.
